svg.title: A diagram consisting of three lines of text, followed by one line of characters and symbols, followed by one more line of text. The lines of text just have vowels showing; the remaining letters are simply full stops. The line of characters and symbols reads: D, DF under a line, a rectangle, 19 F + 44, a right triangle lying on the hypotenuse with a dot at the left corner, 357, and the same triangle flipped horizontally.
